**Version Used**: lab.razor.fyi, sharplab.io, godbolt.org

**Steps to Reproduce**:

```csharp
using System;

switch ((object)(nint)2)
{
    case 2:
        break;
    case (nint)2:
        Console.WriteLine("Case 2");
        goto case (nint)2;
